'''百达翡丽'''（{{lang-en|'''Patek Philippe & Co.'''}}），是[[瑞士|瑞士]]名贵钟表品牌、生产商，于1839年创立，总部位于瑞士[[日內瓦|日內瓦]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/history#1839-1877|title=Patek Philippe {{!}} Company {{!}} History|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=Patek Philippe SA|access-date=2018-11-26|archive-date=2012-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728122613/http://www.patek.ch/contents/default/en/timeline.html#1839-1877|dead-url=no}}</ref> 百达翡丽是世界上最古老的钟表品牌之一，1932年起成为瑞士{{le|斯登家族|Stern family}}的家族企业，其钟表生产历史自创立起从未间断。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pragnell.co.uk/pragnell-house/news/175-years-of-patek-philippe-a-big-story-in-three-chapters|title=175 years of Patek Philippe: A big story in three chapters|language=en|website=www.pragnell.co.uk|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604170044/https://www.pragnell.co.uk/pragnell-house/news/175-years-of-patek-philippe-a-big-story-in-three-chapters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/the-manufacture|title=Patek Philippe {{!}} Company {{!}} The Manufacture|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=Patek Philippe SA|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215223427/https://www.patek.com/en/company/the-manufacture|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/news/the-175th-anniversary|title=Patek Philippe {{!}} News {{!}} Celebrating our 175th Anniversary|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=Patek Philippe SA|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215224955/https://www.patek.com/en/company/news/the-175th-anniversary|dead-url=no}}</ref> 百达翡丽设计并制造钟表产品以及机芯，包括许多世界上最复杂的机械表。该公司目前在世界范围内拥有400余家零售点，在[[亚洲|亚洲]]、[[欧洲|欧洲]]、[[北美洲|北美洲]]及[[大洋洲|大洋洲]]拥有数十家[[分销|分销]]中心，并于2001年在瑞士[[日內瓦|日內瓦]]建立了百达翡丽博物馆。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/retail-service/authorized-retailers|title=Patek Philippe SA {{!}} Authorized Retailers|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=www.patek.com|access-date=2018-05-07|archive-date=2018-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507222448/https://www.patek.com/en/retail-service/authorized-retailers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/retail-service/distributors|title=Patek Philippe SA {{!}} Distributors|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=www.patek.com|access-date=2018-05-07|archive-date=2018-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507222513/https://www.patek.com/en/retail-service/distributors|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/patek-philippe-museum|title=Patek Philippe {{!}} Visit the Patek Philippe Museum in Geneva|accessdate=2018-12-21|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|work=Patek Philippe SA|language=en|archive-date=2018-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230015734/https://www.patek.com/en/company/patek-philippe-museum|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/photo-report--inside-the-patek-philippe-museum--100--photos|title=Photo Report: Inside The Patek Philippe Museum|accessdate=2018-12-21|last=November 4|first=Benjamin Clymer|work=HODINKEE|language=en|archive-date=2018-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221182547/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/photo-report--inside-the-patek-philippe-museum--100--photos|dead-url=no}}</ref>

百达翡丽被普遍視為世界上最负盛名的鐘錶品牌之一。<ref name="Korda2004">{{citation|title=Marking Time: Collecting Watches and Thinking about Time|date=1 January 2004|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9VYKILqUThQC&pg=PA71|quote=|authormask=|author=Michael Korda|origyear=|pages=71–|publisher=Barnes & Noble Publishing|format=|bibcode=|doi=|isbn=978-0-7607-3576-3|oclc=|id=|laysummary=|laydate=|accessdate=2018-12-16|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608200237/https://books.google.com/books?id=9VYKILqUThQC&pg=PA71|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.christies.com/features/5-reasons-collectors-love-Patek-Philippe-7390-1.aspx|title=5 reasons collectors love Patek Philippe {{!}} Christie's|language=en|website=www.christies.com|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214065146/https://www.christies.com/features/5-reasons-collectors-love-Patek-Philippe-7390-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/style/article/patek-philippe-art-of-watches/index.html|title=Why collectors covet Patek Philippe timepieces|date=2017-07-18|last=CNN|first=Steve Dool|language=en|website=CNN Style|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214065732/https://www.cnn.com/style/article/patek-philippe-art-of-watches/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/ricardogeromel/2014/04/15/time-is-money-for-luxury-watchmaker-patek-philippes-swiss-owner-and-now-billionaire-philippe-stern/|title=Luxury Watchmaker Patek Philippe's Swiss Owner Philippe Stern Now A Billionaire|last=Geromel|first=Ricardo|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214065305/https://www.forbes.com/sites/ricardogeromel/2014/04/15/time-is-money-for-luxury-watchmaker-patek-philippes-swiss-owner-and-now-billionaire-philippe-stern/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":46">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/booked/2010/05/07/patek-philippe-in-america-unparalleled-luxury-that-captures-hearts—and-wrists/|title=Patek Philippe in America: Unparalleled Luxury That Captures Hearts—And Wrists|last=Clymer|first=Benjamin|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2013-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020175823/http://www.forbes.com/sites/booked/2010/05/07/patek-philippe-in-america-unparalleled-luxury-that-captures-hearts%E2%80%94and-wrists/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 多年來，百达翡丽的客户及佩戴者中不乏显赫人士，包括英国女王[[维多利亚女王|维多利亚]]、英国女王[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]、[[教皇|教皇]][[庇护九世|庇护九世]]、[[阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦|阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦]]、[[瑪麗·居禮|瑪麗·居禮]]、[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]、[[纳尔逊·曼德拉|纳尔逊·曼德拉]]、[[巴勃羅·畢卡索|毕加索]]、[[柴可夫斯基|柴可夫斯基]]、[[列夫·托爾斯泰|列夫·托尔斯泰]]，等等。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":14">{{Cite web|url=http://patekwatch.blogspot.com/2011/06/queen-elizabeth-custom-patek-philippe.html|title=Queen Elizabeth Custom Patek Philippe Golden Ellipse...|date=2012-06-04|last=Ehrlich|first=Jake|website=...Welcome to PatekMagazine.com...Home of Jake's Patek Philippe World...|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214070934/http://patekwatch.blogspot.com/2011/06/queen-elizabeth-custom-patek-philippe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":25" /><ref name=":58">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/feb/07/nelson-mandela-personal-artefacts-london-exhibition|title=Nelson Mandela's personal artefacts go on show in London|last=Addley|first=Esther|date=2019-02-07|work=The Guardian|access-date=2019-02-09|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2019-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209011033/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/feb/07/nelson-mandela-personal-artefacts-london-exhibition|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":13" /> 截止至2018年， 在{{tsl|en|List of most expensive watches sold at auction|錶類拍賣最高價列表|世界前十的表类拍卖记录}}中，7款由百达翡丽[[腕錶|腕表]]或[[怀表|怀表]]保持。其中，百达翡丽为美国银行家小亨利·格雷夫斯（Henry Graves Jr.）订制的、1989年前世界上最复杂的机械表“亨利·格雷夫斯超复杂怀表（Henry Grave Supercomplication）''”'' 保持世界表类拍卖最高价2400万[[美元|美金]]（23,237,000 [[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]），于2014年11月11日由[[蘇富比|苏富比]]在瑞士日内瓦拍卖售出。<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/arieladams/2014/11/12/24000000-patek-philippe-supercomplication-pocket-watch-beats-its-own-record-at-auction/#39f2160c20dc|title=$24,000,000 Patek Philippe Supercomplication Pocket Watch Beats Its Own Record At Auction|last=Adams|first=Ariel|work=Forbes|language=en|access-date=2018-11-23|archive-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123113531/https://www.forbes.com/sites/arieladams/2014/11/12/24000000-patek-philippe-supercomplication-pocket-watch-beats-its-own-record-at-auction/#39f2160c20dc|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=http://time.com/3578825/expensive-watch-soethbys-patek-philippe/|title=Swiss Pocket Watch Sells for Record $24 Million|language=en|website=Time|access-date=2018-11-23|archive-date=2018-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181205004231/http://time.com/3578825/expensive-watch-soethbys-patek-philippe/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.sothebys.com/en/auctions/ecatalogue/2014/important-watches-ge1404/lot.345.html|title=Patek Philippe (THE HENRY GRAVES JR. SUPERCOMPLICATION)|date=|last=|first=|website=Sotheby's|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924135505/http://www.sothebys.com/en/auctions/ecatalogue/2014/important-watches-ge1404/lot.345.html|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref>

==歷史==

=== 早期历史 ===
[[File:Antoni_Patek.jpg|缩略图]]
[[File:JeanAdrienPhilippe.jpg|缩略图]]
早于16世纪，钟表制造业的深厚文化就已在瑞士[[日内瓦|日内瓦]]萌芽。百达翡丽的创始人[[安托万·帕特克|安托万·帕特克]]（Antoine Patek）原为1831年[[波兰|波兰]]反抗俄国统治的革命者，波兰革命失败后他逃往[[法国|法国]]，后在[[瑞士|瑞士]][[日内瓦|日内瓦]]定居。1839年5月1日，安托万·帕特克和[[波蘭|波蘭]]移民弗朗西斯·查皮克（Franciszek Czapek）於[[日內瓦|日內瓦]]開始製作[[怀表|怀表]]，公司命名为“百达查皮克（Patek, Czapek & Cie）” 。<ref name=":43">{{Cite web|title=Part 1: Patek Philippe - The Journey to Geneva and the Birth of a Legend|url=https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-1-patek-philippe--the-journey-to-geneva-and-the-birth-of-a-legend/|work=www.shreve.com|accessdate=2019-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106104317/https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-1-patek-philippe--the-journey-to-geneva-and-the-birth-of-a-legend/|archive-date=2019-01-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

1845年4月18日，[[安托万·帕特克|安托万·帕特克]]和西斯·查皮克由于分歧而解除了合作关系、公司[[清算|清算]]。<ref name=":352">{{Cite web|url=https://static.patek.com/pdf/others/Patek_Philippe_Museum_Catalog_Preview_Volume_I.pdf|title=Patek Philippe Watches (Volume I) - Patek Philippe Museum|last=|first=|date=|website=Patek Philippe|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114153239/https://static.patek.com/pdf/others/Patek_Philippe_Museum_Catalog_Preview_Volume_I.pdf|archive-date=2019-01-14|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Patek Philippe History – Official Watches|url=https://www.officialwatches.com/patek-philippe/history/|accessdate=2019-02-01|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190113182244/https://www.officialwatches.com/patek-philippe/history/|archive-date=2019-01-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 西斯·查皮克于同年5月1日与新合伙人尤利斯·格鲁泽斯基（Juliusz Gruzewski） 另行创建了制表公司“查皮克（Czapek & Cie）”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://czapek.com/the-history/|title=The History|language=en-US|website=Czapek|access-date=2018-12-22|archive-date=2018-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223131033/https://czapek.com/the-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而安托万·帕特克很快便与法国钟表匠[[阿德里安·菲利普|阿德里安·菲利普]]（Adrien Philippe）在巴黎一个[[展覽會|展览会]]中相遇。当时阿德里安·菲利普已经设计发明出表壳很薄而且上链和调校都不用传统表匙的怀表，该技术在历史上被称为“無匙上條机制（keyless winding mechanism）”。这种怀表在展览会上甚受漠视，而安托万·帕特克却深为其新的设计所吸引。两人经过一番交谈，立即达成合作的意向，安托万·帕特克与阿德里安·菲利普于1845年5月15日成立新公司“百达（Patek & Cie）”。<ref name=":43" /><ref name=":352" />

1851年1月1日，公司正式更名为“百达翡丽（Patek, Philippe & Cie）”。<ref name=":43" />''<ref name=":82">{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/history|title=Patek Philippe SA | History|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=www.patek.com|access-date=2018-05-07|archive-date=2012-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728122613/http://www.patek.ch/contents/default/en/timeline.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>'' 同年，在[[伦敦|伦敦]][[世界博览会|世界博览会]]上，英国[[维多利亚女王|维多利亚女皇]]选中并买下了一枚百达翡丽的无钥式挂表（keyless pendant watch）。<ref name=":83">{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/history|title=Patek Philippe SA {{!}} History|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=www.patek.com|access-date=2018-05-07|archive-date=2012-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728122613/http://www.patek.ch/contents/default/en/timeline.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":22">{{Cite web|url=https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-1-patek-philippe--the-journey-to-geneva-and-the-birth-of-a-legend/|title=Part 1: Patek Philippe - The Journey to Geneva and the Birth of a Legend|website=www.shreve.com|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106104317/https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-1-patek-philippe--the-journey-to-geneva-and-the-birth-of-a-legend/|archive-date=2019-01-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 这只采用新旋柄的挂表悬垂在一根镶有13颗[[钻石|钻石]]的金别针上，珐琅蓝金表盖上饰以钻石拼成的[[玫瑰|玫瑰]]。<ref name=":222">{{Cite web|url=https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-1-patek-philippe--the-journey-to-geneva-and-the-birth-of-a-legend/|title=Part 1: Patek Philippe - The Journey to Geneva and the Birth of a Legend|website=www.shreve.com|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106104317/https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-1-patek-philippe--the-journey-to-geneva-and-the-birth-of-a-legend/|archive-date=2019-01-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 当时，女皇的丈夫[[阿尔伯特亲王|阿尔伯特亲王]]也选购了百达翡丽的一只怀表。名人购精品，百达翡丽由此奠定了其贵族化的地位。

1877年3月，创始人安托万·帕特克逝世、享年65岁，但其子未加入公司。<ref name=":232">{{Cite web|url=https://www.pragnell.co.uk/pragnell-house/news/175-years-of-patek-philippe-a-big-story-in-three-chapters|title=175 years of Patek Philippe: A big story in three chapters|language=en|website=www.pragnell.co.uk|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604170044/https://www.pragnell.co.uk/pragnell-house/news/175-years-of-patek-philippe-a-big-story-in-three-chapters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":242">{{Cite web|url=http://www.brittons-watches.co.uk/NEW_SITE/history_dating/History_Patek.asp|title=History|website=www.brittons-watches.co.uk|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2018-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181231203800/http://www.brittons-watches.co.uk/NEW_SITE/history_dating/History_Patek.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref> 因此，[[阿德里安·菲利普|阿德里安·菲利普]]的女婿约瑟夫·安东尼·贝拿希·翡丽（Joseph Antoine Bénassy-Philippe）继承了安托万·帕特克在公司的职位。<ref name=":232" />1887年，百达翡丽开始采用新的品牌标志并保留至今： 厂标由[[骑士|骑士]]的[[剑|剑]]和[[牧师|牧师]]的[[十字架|十字架]]组合而成，也被称做“卡拉特拉瓦十字架（Calatrava Cross）”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/h/patek-philippe/|title=Patek Philippe|date=|last=|first=|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106104322/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/h/patek-philippe/|archive-date=2019-01-06|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-05}}</ref>它的由来是：1158年，[[西班牙|西班牙]]一个叫卡拉特拉瓦的城市受到[[摩尔人|摩尔人]]的[[侵略|侵略]]，勇敢的牧师雷蒙德和骑士迪哥·贝拉斯凯斯率领民众进行殊死的抗战，最终把摩尔人驱走。牧师（十字架）和骑士（剑），合在一起便成为庄严与勇敢的象征。这象征正好代表着安托万·帕特克与阿德里安·菲利普合作的精神。1891年，76岁的阿德里安·菲利普退休，并将其在公司的职权交予了他最小的儿子约瑟夫·埃梅里·翡丽（Joseph Emile Philippe），以及弗朗西斯·安东尼·孔蒂（Francois Antoine Conty）。<ref name=":232" /><ref name=":242" /> 创始人阿德里安·菲利普于1894年1月去世。<ref name=":242" />

=== 公司改制 ===
1901年，在贝拿希·翡丽和约瑟夫·翡丽的运作下，百达翡丽公司改制成为[[股份有限公司|股份有限公司]]，公司的全名为“百达翡丽制表股份有限公司（Ancienne Manufacture d'horlogerie Patek, Philippe & Cie, Société Anonyme）”。<ref name=":23">{{Cite web|url=https://www.pragnell.co.uk/pragnell-house/news/175-years-of-patek-philippe-a-big-story-in-three-chapters|title=175 years of Patek Philippe: A big story in three chapters|language=en|website=www.pragnell.co.uk|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604170044/https://www.pragnell.co.uk/pragnell-house/news/175-years-of-patek-philippe-a-big-story-in-three-chapters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":24">{{Cite web|url=http://www.brittons-watches.co.uk/NEW_SITE/history_dating/History_Patek.asp|title=History|website=www.brittons-watches.co.uk|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2018-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181231203800/http://www.brittons-watches.co.uk/NEW_SITE/history_dating/History_Patek.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.truefacet.com/guide/beginning-brand-patek-philippe/|title=The History of the Patek Philippe Brand {{!}} The Loupe, TrueFacet|date=2015-09-29|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107124400/https://www.truefacet.com/guide/beginning-brand-patek-philippe/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 百达翡丽公司保持家族式运营同时拥有7位股东，其中5位股东构成了公司的董事会、贝拿希·翡丽任董事会主席。<ref name=":23" /> 之后约瑟夫·翡丽的儿子加入公司，而他也成为了百达翡丽公司中最后一位创始人的后裔。<ref name=":23" /> 1915年，[[阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦|阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦]]向百达翡丽购买了一个金色的怀表，同年他完成了[[广义相对论|广义相对论]]的建立。<ref name=":29">{{Cite web|url=https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-2-patek-philippe--the-evolution-of-pocket-watches-and-ownership/|title=Part 2: Patek Philippe: The Evolution of Pocket Watches and Ownership|website=www.shreve.com|access-date=2019-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190128135215/https://www.shreve.com/blog/part-2-patek-philippe--the-evolution-of-pocket-watches-and-ownership/|archive-date=2019-01-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.watchtime.com/downloads/free-download-watchtime-spotlight-patek-philippe/|title=Patek Philippe, Pocket Watch to Wristwatch: A History of the Patek Philippe Watch Company|last=Friedrich|first=Written byCarina|date=2015-11-10|website=WatchTime - USA's No.1 Watch Magazine|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-27|archive-date=2019-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190128135437/https://www.watchtime.com/downloads/free-download-watchtime-spotlight-patek-philippe/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ias.edu/idea-tags/general-relativity|title=General Relativity|website=Institute for Advanced Study|language=en|access-date=2019-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190128082842/https://www.ias.edu/idea-tags/general-relativity|archive-date=2019-01-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

1932年起，瑞士的斯登家族（Stern family）开始掌控百达翡丽，公司最初由查尔斯·斯登（Charles Stern）和尚·斯登（Jean Stern）两兄弟在[[大萧条时期|大萧条时期]]（Great Depression）收购。<ref name="#1"/><ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=a503a120-fdd5-11e8-bb5a-99c1d4f004ca&url=L2JpbGxpb25haXJlcy9wcm9maWxlcy9waGlsaXBwZS1zdGVybi8=|title=Philippe Stern|date=|last=|first=|website=www.bloomberg.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608222025/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=a503a120-fdd5-11e8-bb5a-99c1d4f004ca&url=L2JpbGxpb25haXJlcy9wcm9maWxlcy9waGlsaXBwZS1zdGVybi8=|archive-date=2019-06-08|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-12-12}}</ref> 斯登兄弟的公司（Fabrique de Cadrans Sterns Frères）此前一直作为百达翡丽公司的生意伙伴，负责为百达翡丽生产、提供表盘。1958年，查尔斯·斯登之子亨利·斯登 （Henri Stern）继任百达翡丽总裁。<ref name=":5"/><ref name=patek_history>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/history|title=Patek Philippe | Company | History|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=Patek Philippe SA|access-date=2018-12-12|archive-date=2012-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728122613/http://www.patek.ch/contents/default/en/timeline.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 近期发展 ===
1993年起，亨利·斯登之子菲利普·斯登（Philippe Stern）成为百达翡丽公司总裁。<ref name=":5"/><ref name=patek_history/> 为取得更进一步的发展，百达翡丽在1996年10月正式发行半年刊《百达翡丽国际杂志（Patek Philippe Magazine）》，以英、法、日、中、德、意6种语言版本发行，力图通过该杂志的内容来吸引客户，提升企业形象。<ref name=":49">{{Cite web|url=https://www.fhs.swiss/eng/2017_01_12_02_Patek.html|title=The «Generations» ad campaign is twenty years old|last=|first=|date=|website=Federation of the Swiss watch industry FH|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226045837/https://www.fhs.swiss/eng/2017_01_12_02_Patek.html|archive-date=2019-02-26|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-02-25}}</ref> 该杂志面向百达翡丽的客户，并接受了众多世界著名作家的稿件，包括诺贝尔文学奖得主[[高行健|高行健]]以及[[若泽·萨拉马戈|若泽·萨拉马戈]]。<ref name=":49" />

2000年后，百达翡丽钟表在世界拍卖市场上的成交价不断走高。截止至2018年12月， 在{{tsl|en|List of most expensive watches sold at auction|錶類拍賣最高價列表|世界前十的表类拍卖记录}}中（均超过500万美金），7款由百达翡丽[[腕錶|腕表]]或[[怀表|怀表]]保持；在世界前58的表类拍卖纪录中（均超过200万美金），有46款由百达翡丽[[腕錶|腕表]]或[[怀表|怀表]]保持。其中，有小部分拍卖价是由百达翡丽自行竞价推高，有些拍卖表款最终被百达翡丽自行购买并收藏入其位于瑞士日内瓦的百达翡丽博物馆中。<ref name="PPWSJ2010">Clerizo, Michael, [http://magazine.wsj.com/gatherer/how-much-is-it-worth/time-honored/ "Watch Auctions: Time Honored: With their mystique, brands like Patek Philippe can command hundreds of thousands of dollars at watch auctions"] {{Wayback|url=http://magazine.wsj.com/gatherer/how-much-is-it-worth/time-honored/ |date=20130918194452 }}, ''[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]'', April 29, 2010</ref><ref name="PPWSJ2007">Frank, Robert, [https://blogs.wsj.com/wealth/2007/10/08/all-that-glitters-may-not-be-gold/ "All That Glitters May Not Be Gold"] {{Wayback|url=https://blogs.wsj.com/wealth/2007/10/08/all-that-glitters-may-not-be-gold/ |date=20181215231024 }}, ''The Wall Street Journal'', October 8, 2007</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.patek.ch/contents/default/en/museum.html|title=PATEK PHILIPPE SA - Welcome to Our Official Website|accessdate=24 May 2016|author=Patek Philippe SA|publisher=|archive-date=2012-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121208202312/http://www.patek.ch/contents/default/en/museum.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年起，菲利蒲·斯登之子蒂埃里·斯登（Thierry Stern）成为公司新任总裁。<ref name="KPMG">[[KPMG|KPMG]], [http://www.kpmg.com.cn/en/virtual_library/Consumer_markets/Consumer_Currents/CC0805.pdf "Standing the Test of Time"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kpmg.com.cn/en/virtual_library/Consumer_markets/Consumer_Currents/CC0805.pdf |date=20170331212237 }}, pp.16-18, in ''Consumer Currents'', Issue 5, 2008, [[KPMG|KPMG International]]</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.prestigemag.co/2016/07/thierry-stern/|title=Thierry Stern - Prestige Magazine|date=2016-07-12|newspaper=Prestige Magazine|language=en-US|access-date=2017-02-06|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207031339/http://www.prestigemag.co/2016/07/thierry-stern/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://robbreport.com/Watches/Patek-Philippe|title=Robb Report|accessdate=2018-12-16|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104173510/http://robbreport.com/Watches/Patek-Philippe|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2010年，百达翡丽年产4万枚时计，而2017年的年产量为5.8万枚。<ref name="KPMG" /><ref name=":34">{{Cite web|url=https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/thierry-stern-you-have-to-innovate-otherwise-you-die/|title=Thierry Stern : «You have to innovate, otherwise you die» – FHH Journal|accessdate=2018-12-30|work=journal.hautehorlogerie.org|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804044419/https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/thierry-stern-you-have-to-innovate-otherwise-you-die/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 据蒂埃里·斯登透露，为保证百达翡丽品牌的质量及稀有度，百达翡丽只会缓慢提高年产量（平均每年1-3%）并且最终不会越过某个限度，其中2018年年产6.2万枚。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-swiss-watches-patek-idUKKCN1MS26M|title=Swiss watchmaker Patek Philippe says Chinese demand still rising|date=2018-10-18|work=Reuters|language=en|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181129140542/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-swiss-watches-patek-idUKKCN1MS26M|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Swiss watchmakers say slowing growth in China won't hurt sales this...|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-swiss-watches-idUSKCN1R22CK|newspaper=Reuters|date=2019-03-21|accessdate=2019-03-23|language=en|archive-date=2019-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323021314/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-swiss-watches-idUSKCN1R22CK|dead-url=no}}</ref> 百达翡丽现为{{link-en|瑞士鐘錶行業聯合會|Federation of the Swiss Watch Industry}}（Federation of the Swiss Watch Industry）的主要成員。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fhs.swiss/eng/watch_brands.html?letter=P|title=Watch brands|date=|last=|first=|website=Federation of the swiss watch industry|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404235042/http://www.fhs.swiss/eng/watch_brands.html?letter=P|archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no|access-date=|accessdate=|author=|publisher=}}</ref>

== 公司标语 ==
