=== Calatrava 腕表 ===
1932年，百达翡丽推出第一款Calatrava 腕表Ref. 96，该腕表由英国制表师大卫·彭尼（David Penny）设计并受到德国包豪斯（Bauhaus）艺术风潮的影响。<ref name=":84">{{Cite web|url=https://www.patek.com/en/company/history|title=Patek Philippe SA {{!}} History (1839 - 1877)|date=|last=GENEVE|first=PATEK PHILIPPE SA|language=en|website=www.patek.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728122613/http://www.patek.ch/contents/default/en/timeline.html|archive-date=2012-07-28|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-05-07}}</ref><ref name=":38">{{Cite web|url=http://www.watchfinder.com/articles/review-patek-philippe-calatrava-tra|title=Review: Patek Philippe Calatrava Travel Time|website=www.watchfinder.com|access-date=2019-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190115132430/https://www.watchfinder.com/articles/review-patek-philippe-calatrava-tra|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":39">{{Cite web|url=https://www.truefacet.com/guide/the-history-of-the-patek-philippe-calatrava/|title=The History of the Patek Philippe Calatrava {{!}} The Loupe, TrueFacet|date=2018-10-12|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190115023051/https://www.truefacet.com/guide/the-history-of-the-patek-philippe-calatrava/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 最初在1932年收购百达翡丽后，斯登兄弟迅速推出该表款，以期帮助公司顺利度过[[大萧条时期|大萧条时期]]。<ref name=":38" /><ref name=":40">{{Cite web|url=https://ph.asiatatler.com/style/patek-philippe-and-its-german-art-movement-connection|title=Patek Philippe And Its German Art Movement Connection|date=2017-10-11|last=Lim|first=Terence|language=en|website=Philippine Tatler|access-date=2019-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190115023447/https://ph.asiatatler.com/style/patek-philippe-and-its-german-art-movement-connection|dead-url=no}}</ref>

最早的Calatrava Ref.96腕表持续生产了40余年，它的继承表款包括Ref. 2526, Ref. 3520, Ref. 5196 等等。<ref name=":39" /><ref name=":41">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/the-patek-philippe-2526-and-why-its-a-watch-to-pay-attention-to|title=In-Depth: The Patek Philippe 2526, And Why It's A Watch To Pay Attention To|last=May 18|first=Benjamin Clymer|language=en|last2=2016|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2019-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190115132505/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/the-patek-philippe-2526-and-why-its-a-watch-to-pay-attention-to|dead-url=no}}</ref> Calatrava 系列腕表以其简洁高雅的设计而著称，一经推出就成为了百达翡丽的旗舰表款之一。<ref name=":40" /><ref name=":41" /> 值得注意的是，卡拉特拉瓦十字架（Calatrava Cross）从1887年起就是百达翡丽公司的注册商标。 <ref name=":37">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/h/patek-philippe/|title=Patek Philippe|date=|last=|first=|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106104322/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/h/patek-philippe/|archive-date=2019-01-06|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-05}}</ref>

=== 世界时系列腕表 ===
[[File:Patek_Philippe_5131R-001_World_Time_in_Rose_Gold.jpg|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Patek_Philippe_5131R-001_World_Time_in_Rose_Gold.jpg]]
百达翡丽世界时系列腕表（World Time/Heures Universelles）最早于1939年推出，第一批的系列标号为Ref. 1415。<ref name=":18">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/the-patek-philippe-mens-world-time-ref-5230g-new-york-2017-special|title=Introducing: The Patek Philippe World Time Ref. 5230G New York 2017 Limited Edition|last=July 12|first=Jack Forster|language=en|last2=2017|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2019-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105201026/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/the-patek-philippe-mens-world-time-ref-5230g-new-york-2017-special|dead-url=no}}</ref> 世界时这项复杂功能可以在一块手表上显示世界24个[[时区|时区]]的时间，由瑞士制表师路易·柯蒂亚（Louis Cottier）在20世界30年代发明。<ref name=":18" /><ref name=":19">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/msolomon/2015/06/17/best-worldtimer-watches-2015-gmt-utc-world-time-watches/|title=The World of Worldtimer Watches|last=Solomon|first=Michael|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2019-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105200913/https://www.forbes.com/sites/msolomon/2015/06/17/best-worldtimer-watches-2015-gmt-utc-world-time-watches/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 柯蒂亚的发明受到了许多制表公司的关注，其中百达翡丽是第一个在与柯蒂亚先生合作后推出世界时系列腕表的公司。<ref name=":19" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.europastar.com/time-keeper/1004090024-world-time-patek-philippe-and-louis-cottier.html|title=World time: Patek Philippe and Louis Cottier|language=en|website=www.europastar.com|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2019-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105200944/https://www.europastar.com/time-keeper/1004090024-world-time-patek-philippe-and-louis-cottier.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> Ref. 1415的继承表款包括Ref. 2523，Ref. 5230，Ref. 5531（含[[语音报时|三问报时]]），等等。<ref name=":18" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/robertanaas/2017/07/12/patek-philippe-unveils-560000-world-first-world-time-minute-repeater-watch-at-grand-exhibitionny/|title=Patek Philippe Unveils $560,000 World Time Minute Repeater Watch at Grand Exhibition, New York|last=Naas|first=Roberta|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106055223/https://www.forbes.com/sites/robertanaas/2017/07/12/patek-philippe-unveils-560000-world-first-world-time-minute-repeater-watch-at-grand-exhibitionny/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

截止至2018年12月，{{tsl|en|List of most expensive watches sold at auction|錶類拍賣最高價列表|世界200万美金以上的表类拍卖纪录中}}（共有58枚），百达翡丽世界时腕表（Ref. 1415, Ref. 2523）独占6席。其中，2002年4月13日[[安帝古倫拍賣行|安帝古伦拍卖行]]（Antiquorum）拍卖出一枚 Ref. 1415 腕表，创造了该表款的最高拍卖价403万美金（6,603,500 瑞士法郎）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/patek-philippe-ref-ref-1415-lot-26-608|title=Patek Philippe & Cie, Genève, No. 929693, case No. 656462, Ref. 1415 HU (Heures Universelles).|date=|last=|first=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123154305/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/patek-philippe-ref-ref-1415-lot-26-608|archive-date=2018-11-23|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/2008/02/28/most-expensive-watches-forbeslife-time08-cx_nr_0229watch_slide.html|title=By The Numbers: The World's Most Expensive Watches|last=Ruiz|first=Nicola|work=Forbes|access-date=2018-11-23|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410232859/https://www.forbes.com/2008/02/28/most-expensive-watches-forbeslife-time08-cx_nr_0229watch_slide.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 鹦鹉螺系列腕表 ===
1976年，百达翡丽决定推出鹦鹉螺系列腕表（Nautilus），作为公司运动系列的最高级表款。<ref name=patek_history/><ref name=":21">{{Cite web|url=https://www.christies.com/features/Secrets-of-the-Patek-Philippe-Nautilus-7706-1.aspx|title=Secrets of the Patek Philippe Nautilus {{!}} Christie's|language=en|website=www.christies.com|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106055209/https://www.christies.com/features/Secrets-of-the-Patek-Philippe-Nautilus-7706-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> 最早的鹦鹉螺系列表款为Ref. 3700，表壳采用钢材料。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://monochrome-watches.com/history-patek-philippe-nautilus-part-1-nautilus-3700/|title=History of the Patek Philippe Nautilus, Part 1 - The Birth of an Icon, the 3700 (1976/1990)|date=2016-10-11|language=en-US|website=Monochrome Watches|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106104408/https://monochrome-watches.com/history-patek-philippe-nautilus-part-1-nautilus-3700/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该表款由瑞士制表师杰罗·尊达（Gérald Genta）设计，而他之前也为[[愛彼|爱彼]]公司设计了皇家橡树系列（Royal Oak）腕表。百达翡丽公司于[[石英危机|石英危机]]（quartz crisis）期间推出鹦鹉螺系列腕表，以期重新点燃人们对瑞士高端机械表的热情。<ref name=":21" />  

鹦鹉螺系列腕表在百达翡丽公司的营销策略中扮演了重要角色，它不仅承接了公司的悠久传统，也彰显了新生代的活力。<ref>{{Citation|title=History of the Patek Philippe Nautilus, 2015|url=http://www.timeandwatches.com/p/history-of-patek-philippe-nautilus.html|accessdate=2019-01-30|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426071926/https://www.timeandwatches.com/p/history-of-patek-philippe-nautilus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 鹦鹉螺系列表款已成为百达翡丽最受欢迎的系列之一。<ref name=":21" /><ref name=":33">{{Cite web|url=https://www.watchtime.com/featured/luxury-in-steel-a-history-of-the-patek-philippe-nautilus/|title=Luxury in Steel: A History of the Patek Philippe Nautilus|date=2018-12-14|last=Koch|first=Written byJens|language=en-US|website=WatchTime - USA's No.1 Watch Magazine|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210072846/https://www.watchtime.com/featured/luxury-in-steel-a-history-of-the-patek-philippe-nautilus/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其中，公司于2006年推出的鹦鹉螺Ref. 5711、Ref. 5712已成为最受欢迎的款式之一，该表款是百达翡丽公司为纪念鹦鹉螺系列诞生30周年而推出的。<ref name=":21" /><ref name=":33" />

=== 万年历计时腕表 ===

百达翡丽万年历计时最早于1941年推出，第一款为Ref. 1518。<ref name=":9" /> 2016年11月12日，一枚钢制的Ref. 1518在富藝斯拍卖行（Phillips）售出，成交价约1114万美金 (11,002,000 瑞士法郎)，成为世界拍卖市场最贵腕表（记录保持到2017年10月）。<ref name=":30" /> 该腕表是钢制Ref. 1518（共4枚）第一次出现在世界拍卖市场上。<ref name=":31" />

作为Ref. 1518的继承表款，Ref. 2499腕表被广泛认为是世界上最伟大的腕表系列之一。<ref name=":9">{{Cite web|url=https://www.christies.com/features/Patek-Philippe-perpetual-chronograph-wristwatches-7654-1.aspx|title=Collecting guide: Patek Philippe perpetual chronograph wristwatches {{!}} Christie's|language=en|website=www.christies.com|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2018-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181207171457/https://www.christies.com/Features/Patek-Philippe-perpetual-chronograph-wristwatches-7654-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":10">{{Cite web|url=https://www.sothebys.com/en/articles/one-of-the-most-important-vintage-wristwatches-in-the-world|title=One of the Most Important Vintage Wristwatches in the World|date=|last=|first=|website=Sotheby's|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216031605/https://www.sothebys.com/en/articles/one-of-the-most-important-vintage-wristwatches-in-the-world|archive-date=2018-12-16|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.phillipswatches.com/geneva-auction-highlight-the-rose-gold-patek-philippe-ref-2499-third-series/|title=Geneva Auction Highlight: The Rose Gold Patek Philippe Ref. 2499 (Third Series) {{!}} PHILLIPS|website=www.phillipswatches.com|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216031321/https://www.phillipswatches.com/geneva-auction-highlight-the-rose-gold-patek-philippe-ref-2499-third-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/rose-gold-2499-most-expensive-watch-on-the-internet|title=Found: A Rose Gold Patek Philippe 2499 For Sale (Sidenote: Is This The Most Expensive Wristwatch Ever Listed For Sale Online?)|last=August 14|first=Benjamin Clymer|language=en|last2=2014|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216073758/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/rose-gold-2499-most-expensive-watch-on-the-internet|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://watchtime.me/the-knowledge/article/1151/patek-philippe-ref-2499-a-brief-history-of-a-classic|title=Patek Philippe Ref. 2499: A Brief History of a Classic|language=en|website=watchtime|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216031303/http://watchtime.me/the-knowledge/article/1151/patek-philippe-ref-2499-a-brief-history-of-a-classic|dead-url=no}}</ref> 历史上，1950年至1985年间百达翡丽只生产过349枚Ref. 2499腕表、平均一年生产9枚。<ref name=":9" /><ref name=":10" /> 35年间，百达翡丽先后推出了4个子系列的Ref. 2499腕表，对世界其它著名钟表生产商的表款设计及制造影响巨大。<ref name=":9" /> 截止至2018年，{{tsl|en|List of most expensive watches sold at auction|錶類拍賣最高價列表|世界200万美金以上的表类拍卖纪录中}}（共有58枚），百达翡丽Ref. 2499腕表独占11席，同时至少有17枚Ref. 2499腕表在世界拍卖市场上拍出150万美金以上的成交价。其中，2018年11月13日[[苏富比|苏富比]]拍卖出一枚“Asprey Ref. 2499腕表”，创造了该表款的最高拍卖价388万美金（3,915,000 瑞士法郎）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sothebys.com/en/auctions/ecatalogue/2018/important-watches-ge1804/lot.220.html|title=Patek Philippe (RETAILED BY ASPREY: REF 2499)|date=|last=|first=|website=Sotheby's|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127110310/http://www.sothebys.com/en/auctions/ecatalogue/2018/important-watches-ge1804/lot.220.html|archive-date=2018-11-27|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref> Ref. 2499的继承表款包括（按照时间顺序）Ref. 3970，Ref. 5970 以及 Ref. 5270。<ref name=":9" /> 

=== 天文陀飞轮腕表 ===
[[File:Patek-Philippe_MG_2583.jpg|缩略图]]腕表Ref. 5002|替代=]]百达翡丽天文陀飞轮腕表（Sky Moon Tourbillon）于2001年推出, ，亦称天月天文陀飞轮，第一款编号为Ref. 5002。<ref name=":47">{{Cite web|url=http://www.sothebys.com/en/auctions/ecatalogue/2014/important-watches-n09159/lot.30.html|title=THE TITANIUM COLLECTION: Patek Philippe 5001T|last=|first=|date=|website=Sotheby's|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129181312/http://www.sothebys.com/en/auctions/ecatalogue/2014/important-watches-n09159/lot.30.html|archive-date=2019-01-29|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-29}}</ref><ref name=":48">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/elizabethdoerr/2013/05/30/the-patek-philippe-sky-moon-tourbillon-earns-a-place-in-horological-history/|title=The Patek Philippe Sky Moon Tourbillon Earns A Place In Horological History|last=Doerr|first=Elizabeth|website=Forbes|language=en|access-date=2019-01-28|archive-date=2019-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129064236/https://www.forbes.com/sites/elizabethdoerr/2013/05/30/the-patek-philippe-sky-moon-tourbillon-earns-a-place-in-horological-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该表款拥有双面表盘、12项复杂功能，比如[[陀飞轮|陀飞轮]]、[[语音报时|三问报时]]、星空图、月相及轨道。 2013年，公司推出第二款天文陀飞轮Ref. 6002，该表款也拥有12项复杂功能。<ref name=":47" />

天文陀飞轮腕表在2014年前一直是百达翡丽最复杂的腕表，该腕表也是21世纪世界上最重要的腕表之一。<ref name=":47" /><ref name=":48" /> 据估计，百达翡丽每年只生产3-5枚天文陀飞轮腕表，每块售价至少120万美金。<ref name=":48" /> 特别的是，每块天文陀飞轮的购买需要购买者向公司递交申请，并得到百达翡丽总裁蒂埃里·斯登（Thierry Stern）的批准。<ref name=":51">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2013/09/13/1-million-watchand-you-have-to-apply-to-buy-it.html|title=$1 million watch—and you have to apply to buy it!|last=Frank|first=Robert|date=2013-09-13|website=www.cnbc.com|access-date=2019-01-30|archive-date=2019-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190131041926/https://www.cnbc.com/2013/09/13/1-million-watchand-you-have-to-apply-to-buy-it.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":522">{{Cite web|url=https://www.revolution.watch/live-images-full-report-patek-philippe-launches-the-sky-moon-tourbillon-ref-6002g-in-geneva/|title=Patek Philippe Launches The Sky Moon Tourbillon {{!}} Revolution Watch|date=2013-06-01|website=Revolution|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-30}}</ref> 其中，2018年10月2日，一枚天文陀飞轮腕表Ref. 6002G 由[[保利集团|保利拍卖行]]在[[香港|香港]]拍卖售出，最终成交价约271万美金（21,240,000港币）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.polyauction.com.hk/en/buy-and-sell/auctions/lot-listings/194/details/28550/?currencyType=USD|title=Patek Philippe {{!}} Poly Auction Hong Kong|website=www.polyauction.com.hk|access-date=2019-01-28|archive-date=2018-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181124162239/https://www.polyauction.com.hk/en/buy-and-sell/auctions/lot-listings/194/details/28550/?currencyType=USD|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 150周年纪念款 ===
1989年，为纪念150周年店庆，百达翡丽推出Calibre 89怀表，该怀表拥有33项复杂功能，成为世界上有史以来最复杂的机械表（记录保持直到2015年）。<ref>[http://shopping.yahoo.com/articles/yshoppingarticles/671/the-9-most-important-watches-in-the-world/ The 9 Most Important Watches in the World] {{Wayback|url=http://shopping.yahoo.com/articles/yshoppingarticles/671/the-9-most-important-watches-in-the-world/ |date=20120515215745 }} John Biggs,  Popular Mechanics</ref> Calibre 89共4枚，分别为白金款、黄金款、玫瑰金款以及铂金款。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-patek-philippe-caliber-89-for-sale-at-christies-new-york|title=Hands-On: A Patek Philippe Caliber 89, For Sale At Christie's New York|last=May 23|first=Jack Forster|language=en|last2=2016|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123112127/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-patek-philippe-caliber-89-for-sale-at-christies-new-york|archive-date=2018-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/sothebys-patek-philippe-caliber-89-may-2017|title=Auction Report: Patek Philippe Caliber 89 Fails To Sell (Again)|last=May 14|first=Arthur Touchot|language=en|last2=2017|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216031219/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/sothebys-patek-philippe-caliber-89-may-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其中黄金款以及白金款在[[安帝古倫拍賣行|安帝古伦拍卖行]]分别于2009年及2004年拍卖售出，售价均超过500万美金，在{{tsl|en|List of most expensive watches sold at auction|錶類拍賣最高價列表|世界表类拍卖纪录中}}均位列前十。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/patek-philippe-lot-222-364?browse_all=1&page=1&q=Patek+Philippe+Calibre+89|title=The Yellow Gold Calibre 89 Patek Philippe|date=|last=|first=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181124003703/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/patek-philippe-lot-222-364?browse_all=1&page=1&q=Patek+Philippe+Calibre+89|archive-date=2018-11-24|dead-url=yes|access-date=2018-11-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-patek-philippe-caliber-89-for-sale-at-christies-new-york|title=Hands-On: A Patek Philippe Caliber 89, For Sale At Christie's New York - HODINKEE|work=HODINKEE|language=en|access-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123112127/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-patek-philippe-caliber-89-for-sale-at-christies-new-york|archive-date=2018-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/patek-philippe-lot-51-301?browse_all=1&page=2&q=Patek+Philippe+Calibre+89|title=Patek, Philippe, Genève. The white gold "Calibre 89"|date=|last=|first=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181124003638/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/patek-philippe-lot-51-301?browse_all=1&page=2&q=Patek+Philippe+Calibre+89|archive-date=2018-11-24|dead-url=yes|access-date=2018-11-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.jckonline.com/editorial-article/patek-philippe-calibre-89-sold-for-5-million/|title=Patek Philippe Calibre 89 sold for $5 million|work=JCK|language=en-US|access-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123112137/https://www.jckonline.com/editorial-article/patek-philippe-calibre-89-sold-for-5-million/|archive-date=2018-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 175周年纪念款 ===
2014年，为纪念175周年店庆，百达翡丽推出大师弦音腕表Ref. 5175（Grandmaster Chime Ref. 5175），成为百达翡丽公司有史以来生产的最复杂机械腕表、拥有20项复杂功能（不含[[陀飞轮|陀飞轮]]）。<ref name=":42">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=39e75fb0-fd91-11e8-9399-6561e478d2a5&url=L25ld3MvMjAxNC0xMC0xMy9wYXRlay1waGlsaXBwZS11bnZlaWxzLWdyYW5kbWFzdGVyLWNoaW1lLXRoZS13b3JsZC1zLW1vc3QtY29tcGxpY2F0ZWQtd3Jpc3R3YXRjaC1ldmVyLS5odG1s|title=Patek Philippe Unveils Grandmaster Chime: The World's Most Complicated Wristwatch (Ever)|date=|last=|first=|website=www.bloomberg.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216114801/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=39e75fb0-fd91-11e8-9399-6561e478d2a5&url=L25ld3MvMjAxNC0xMC0xMy9wYXRlay1waGlsaXBwZS11bnZlaWxzLWdyYW5kbWFzdGVyLWNoaW1lLXRoZS13b3JsZC1zLW1vc3QtY29tcGxpY2F0ZWQtd3Jpc3R3YXRjaC1ldmVyLS5odG1s|archive-date=2018-12-16|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-12-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/introducing-patek-philippe-grandmaster-chime-ref-5175r|title=Introducing The Patek Philippe Grandmaster Chime Ref. 5175R, Their Most Complicated Wristwatch Yet|last=October 21|first=Evald Muraj|language=en|last2=2014|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215224826/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/introducing-patek-philippe-grandmaster-chime-ref-5175r|dead-url=no}}</ref> 大师弦音腕表Ref. 5175共7枚，其中1枚永久保留在位于瑞士[[日内瓦|日内瓦]]的百达翡丽博物馆中，其余每枚售价约为250万美金。<ref name=":42" /><ref name=":32">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2014/10/14/patek-philippe-unveils-26m-watch.html|title=Patek Philippe unveils $2.6M watch|date=2014-10-14|last=Wright|first=Erica|website=www.cnbc.com|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214182936/https://www.cnbc.com/2014/10/14/patek-philippe-unveils-26m-watch.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

